			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div>Anybody air soft here? <br />
<br />
I went PBalling about 12 years ago, and never did again, and then about 8 years ago, it seemed no one really PBalled anymore, and its all since changed to airsoft. <br />
<br />
Whatever the case may be, they both interest me, but it seems like the only thing in the area for me, here, might be airsoft. <br />
<br />
How much of a money sink is necessary to just begin the hobby? I don't want to jump right into gettng grenade launchers - but instead, just the most basic safety gear, and a decent pistol and perhaps a decent semi automatic rifle, and thats it - nothing on the deluxe/premium line - just something slightly accurate that isn't 100% durable, that I can just keep my hands on.</div>

